net.hudup.core.logistic

Class ValueTriple

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.logistic.ValueTriple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ValueTriple
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a triple which has one integer key key and two double values such as value1 and value2. The @link #value1} and value2 are also called 1-value and 2-value, respectively.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
